{"tid":1738631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比人抄左牌既手足入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:26:12.000Z","uid":320737,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a82ec56af8de09e2741c66a57f5ed68f30d15da8","tid":1738631,"uid":320737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"唔好以為抄左牌放左你走就冇事<br />\n黑警會係呢段時間不停搜証<br />\n然後會向法庭申請搜查令上門拘捕<br />\n時間大約係兩個月至三個月後<br />\n多數由一班唔想上前線既黑警做搜証<br />\n一team人付責一個人既case <br />\n包括CID O記 等等一D完全唔關事既部門都用黎搜你証 呢段時間入面佢地絕對有能力掌握你一切既資訊 就算你冇比到電話號碼佢佢地都有你電話 最好準備一張全新卡+全新iphone <br />\n出門口小心d 甚至有機會比人跟 揾埋你d隊友<br />\n<br />\n唔好問我點知的<br />\n小心為上 記住一日無証據 佢地一日奈你唔何"},{"pid":"a566bf869510107d67e30666c711d6401deb1011","tid":1738631,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8799327a862bfccd75b64f5f553e30e4a9b359f8","tid":1738631,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"一定會target啲人跟蹤搜查令"},{"pid":"567636d4d761a7416fab9c4af7b7a7da3c18916f","tid":1738631,"uid":320737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8799327a862bfccd75b64f5f553e30e4a9b359f8","tid":1738631,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"一定會target啲人跟蹤搜查令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"我本身唔係p牌 因為安全起見叫連仔del左我舊ac<br />\n推唔到post  （雖然我呢d廢話可能個個都知 ）"},{"pid":"cd2e5dd65e9934e6b1e90267138917674157cdaf","tid":1738631,"uid":320737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"仲有 poly附近一帶既cctv都會影低曬比黑警睇<br />\n你地做過d乜 如果自問好易比人對到既 自己小心d"},{"pid":"6313c7e25b40f6a61bf1cf8ae89ede2552d59af5","tid":1738631,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:24:1